{"tid":2232403,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"性侵姊妹花遭通緝又闖民宅性侵母女　富少遭判無期徒刑","createTime":"2020-10-06T10:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T12:20:48.000Z","uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5faed6006722cf079c6b3344ae5a5a991960838a","tid":2232403,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:54:02.000Z","msg":"新北市一名淫魔富少李允然（40歲），2004年就曾假藉科技公司老闆名義徵才，面試時下藥性侵4名女子，惡性重大服刑至2013年才假釋出獄。沒想到他不但沒有悔改，去年7月間在宜蘭性侵一對小模姐妹遭通緝，今年2月警方追捕時李闖入民宅，甚性侵民宅裡的母女，泯滅人性的惡行實在天理難容，最後警方終於在3月將他逮捕到案，宜蘭地方法院判李男處無期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查，李允然家境富裕時不時向父母伸手要錢，2004年他成立空殼科技公司，在飲料與紅酒內下藥性侵，藉此對女員工以及來面試的女子性侵，當時至少有4名女子慘遭毒手，其中年紀最小的被害人才剛滿18歲，事後遭警方逮捕入獄，直到2013年才假釋出獄，近十年牢獄生活與強制治療，李不但沒有悔改，竟又犯下多件令人髮指的性侵案。"},{"pid":"170d917c6032c0b3ace770fdc77e3820718dc06e","tid":2232403,"uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"李允然出獄後又故技重施，仗著父母有錢成立空殼健康國際公司與交友科技公司，把自己塑造成成功的創業青年，還加入許多外拍社團，藉此可接多觸模特兒與網紅，讓他可以趁此機會伸出魔爪，滿足他變態的需求。<br />\n<br />\n去年7月，李允然以拍廣告為名目，以5千元代價邀約一對小模姐妹到宜蘭民宿拍攝，期間在給姐妹倆喝的瓶裝水內摻入安眠藥，迷昏她們後趁機性侵得逞，姐妹兩人醒來後向警方報案求助，宜蘭警方事後屢傳他不到函送地檢署，李依然不到庭應訊，直到今年2月遭地檢署發布通緝。"},{"pid":"57124afaad57076a830d293b239506ae2c3419b6","tid":2232403,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"母女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條撚樣勁識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45032821e16e8509854263f5ef4eaa090e52f9e9","tid":2232403,"uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"宜蘭分局警方2月間確認其通緝身分，持拘票前往李允然新北市住處要將他逮捕歸案，卻在住處搜索時被李奪門而出逃跑，警方的疏忽竟成為另一家人惡夢的開始，宜蘭分局事後也懲處相關人員。<br />\n<br />\n李逃跑後還去購買改造手槍，跑到鄰居家中躲藏整整兩天一夜，期間拿槍恐嚇鄰居母女，將他們全家4人捆綁囚禁、痛毆男主人，並以「殺你全家」作要脅，最變態的是分別拿槍威脅母親與未成年女兒，利用她們互相保護的心多次性侵得逞，最後搜刮全家人9千元現金才離開。<br />\n<br />\n李允然離開後又心生歹念，認為自己會被警察追捕逃亡，都是因為先前小模對他提告性侵，所以決定進行報復，他假冒他人身分再次用拍廣告名目騙小模出來，將小模強押到汽車旅館電擊凌虐且多次性侵得逞，還要求小模要撤回告訴不然「殺死妳」，小模被脅迫後只好就範才獲釋放。<br />\n<br />\n直到3月，警方得知李允然常到新北市板橋一間養生館消費，為防他再次逃脫，警方派出大批警力前往埋伏，終於將他逮捕，依強制性交等罪將他移送地檢署，檢察官認為他涉犯重罪且有逃亡事實將他聲押獲准至今，經法院審理後判處無期徒刑、褫奪公權終生，全案可上訴。（突發中心／宜蘭報導）"},{"pid":"6739545aeaa3b2f5890d51b70e4585822609dc1a","tid":2232403,"uid":154406,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"57124afaad57076a830d293b239506ae2c3419b6","tid":2232403,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"母女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條撚樣勁識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:56:02.000Z","msg":"仲玩埋姊妹花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50416ec96a440693ae56f1d347c5d627fdd88a6","tid":2232403,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景"},{"pid":"7355ad44081261639715be3ae05838d138c2a07c","tid":2232403,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11b778173e971f11fe4a54cf937977c5c7dc7e1","tid":2232403,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7355ad44081261639715be3ae05838d138c2a07c","tid":2232403,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"文盲？"},{"pid":"f8bfb00358a3999b1a8e3abcebe8c1b5d92ec406","tid":2232403,"uid":24181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:00:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">新北市</span>"},{"pid":"d66737e121c17f080dfb99639bece124562f6adf","tid":2232403,"uid":20362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"好撚癲<br />\n最癲係比人通緝仲可以大遙大擺行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e870783d9cd271a25d10f8c2bda3fec04c3167c","tid":2232403,"uid":379830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:05:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"066412c1f2241e5b5b89c736de44921a296d7a96","tid":2232403,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"真 GTA <br />\n<br />\nwasted"},{"pid":"164b2d2aa164297a7273bfb0321375801592fc2b","tid":2232403,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀 去...."},{"pid":"6d30cf30285bdf07cf499e7e13d9fe28e9eae1b8","tid":2232403,"uid":305638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:11:09.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦！人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲！愛她就去搞她，喜歡就強姦啊！表白有什麼用？還是會被拒絕，追不到就強姦，強姦不到就下藥，翻臉就發裸照。大不了蹲監獄咯。你連監獄都不敢蹲，還有什麼資格說你很愛她？出來後繼續強姦她，強姦到她開始懷疑人生，讓她覺得人生的意義就是被你強姦。你們就可以在一起了......<br />\n<br />\n真人版"},{"pid":"7edcc67b63bf6fab8fd192f800947b85d5f3d2df","tid":2232403,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71666dd04ee509d92f1eba3046f614efe09eaf0d","tid":2232403,"uid":14706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:16:01.000Z","msg":"其實強姦4名女子判刑果下已經要強制結紮喇 害死後面果對母女同咩一對小模姐妹"},{"pid":"a50da29345ffe4497d28f2259c9740aaf0c83e9b","tid":2232403,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7355ad44081261639715be3ae05838d138c2a07c","tid":2232403,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52edaa37e710db0b06fdab02173c53db6c19fa9","tid":2232403,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7355ad44081261639715be3ae05838d138c2a07c","tid":2232403,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:30:05.000Z","msg":"眼殘定腦殘？"},{"pid":"437c7fb706c173152c5d707639b88349269a28d4","tid":2232403,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:20:48.000Z","msg":"新北d男人食乜大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}